"},"text":"section 53101 of this title","children":[],"tail":". Those portions of title VI not repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/304"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–304","children":[],"tail":" and sections 802 and 809(a) of the Act were repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/120/tIII/s313/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–120, title III, § 313(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-02-08"},"text":"Feb. 8, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/58"},"text":"130 Stat. 58","children":[],"tail":". Section 801 of the Act was transferred to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t46/s57522"},"text":"section 57522 of this title","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/120/tIII/s313/c/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–120, title III, § 313(c)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-02-08"},"text":"Feb. 8, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/58"},"text":"130 Stat. 58","children":[],"tail":". For complete classification of the Act to the Code, see Tables. For disposition of sections of the former Appendix to Title 46, see Disposition Table preceding "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t46/s101"},"text":"section 101 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
